document_data.Notable Inhabitants:
* [[Agin Lamarck]], an historian and [[book]]-merchant that maintained a shop in [[Podol's Plaza]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Scroll Thief|11}}
* [[Fengor]], a powerful [[illusionist]] that took up residence within [[Kovel Mansion]] during the city's occupation during the early 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
* [[Marten Foss]], a retired adventurer that had a strong admiration for the hero [[Ren o' the Blade]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Scroll Thief|10}}
